Description: Provides modern, tidyverse-style wrapper functions for commonly used
    bioinformatics tools and workflows. The package is designed to streamline and
    standardize tasks in transcriptomics, single-cell RNA-seq, epigenomics, and
    other multi-omics analyses. 
